5. Report and Analytics
5.1 Sales Report
The system shall allow administrators to generate a report of all bookings and payments within a user-specified date range.
5.2 Package Performance Report
The system shall generate a report showing the most and least popular travel packages based on the number of bookings.
5.4 Customer Insight Report
The system shall provide a list of top customers based on their booking frequency or total spending.